com.equinox

Class Signal

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.equinox.Signal

  • public class Signal
extends java.lang.Object
    The Signal Class is used as a container for the messages displayed to the user at the end of an operation. It also contains the formats for different signals.

    paradite
